freesynergy-community-description =
    The FreeSynergy Community repository is an additional Store source for packages
    contributed by the community.

    It extends the default Store with extra themes, widgets, bots, language packs,
    and third-party service integrations. The repository is maintained by community
    contributors and reviewed by the FreeSynergy team before packages are published.
    Adding this repository expands what is available in your Store.

freesynergy-community-features =
    - Additional themes and icon sets
    - Community-contributed widgets
    - Extra language packs
    - Third-party service integrations
    - Reviewed by the FreeSynergy team
    - Open for community contributions via GitHub
